metadata.name: Hublot | Murakami – Rubies
metadata.description: The Hublot | Murakami – Rubies is inspired by Japanese video games & TV from the 1970s as well as the Classic Fusion Takashi Murakami All Black, the first collaboration between Hublot and Takashi Murakami. This NFT is linked to a limited edition unique Classic Fusion watch. Terms and conditions apply : https://boutique.hublot.com/terms-and-conditions-murakami-unique-pieces-nfts
